    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plain-woven fabric of any fiber or blend, with crosswise ribs that typically gives a corded surface.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
